cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to extract information from biomedical texts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural networks (cs.NE) which are also relevant sub-categories.
